Class ContextCollector

java.lang.Object
  org.openrdf.query.algebra.helpers.QueryModelVisitorBase<java.lang.Exception>
      com.clarkparsia.openrdf.query.sparql.ContextCollector
All Implemented Interfaces:
QueryModelVisitor<java.lang.Exception>
public class ContextCollector
extends QueryModelVisitorBase<java.lang.Exception>

Visitor implementation for the sesame query algebra which walks the tree and figures out the context for nodes in the algebra. The context for a node is set on the highest node in the tree. That is, everything below it shares the same context.

Since:
0.3
Version:
0.4
Author:
Blazej Bulka
